    <item>
      <title>美国小企业对盈利的乐观情绪升至五个月高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/us-small-business-optimism-rises-to-five-month-high-on-earnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[12 月份美国小企业的乐观情绪升至五个月高点，主要反映了对销售、盈利趋势和经济预期的悲观情绪有所减轻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/us-small-business-optimism-rises-to-five-month-high-on-earnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
